{"tid":2350240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"勒索工程公司拜神費被拒，荃灣二陂坊勝和惡男吹雞斬人刑毀","createTime":"2021-01-02T07:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T08:21:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0819d45b5d02883abd3b50afcb95b3ee3fe8497c","tid":2350240,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=enyFDDz5Ecg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DenyFDDz5Ecg&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb0z632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ebb0ebfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=enyFDDz5Ecg</a><br />\n<br />\n近兩個月內，長沙灣和新蒲崗兩個工廠區，接連有負責大廈維修的工程公司，被人刑毀破壞，又有公司東主被襲擊打傷。有江湖消息指出，涉及今次刑毀恐嚇的黑幫，是活躍於荃灣二陂坊的和勝和人馬，一名名為「大舊」的小頭目。而「大舊」正是早前在尖沙咀被槍擊的勝和猛人「黐線勇」的門生。"},{"pid":"dd8e620c80d50a826b9da1449e861882722af50e","tid":2350240,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"黐線勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92edd1527fde9c87a0e5c8fe113a904ed488f443","tid":2350240,"uid":127067,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:09:37.000Z","msg":"呢班仆街肯拉未"},{"pid":"c03d05966c471bd24dec7b6d1e617f6a53b47f98","tid":2350240,"uid":129676,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"咁多大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193415d47a9adda77ee42cd378cc3683465341aa","tid":2350240,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd8e620c80d50a826b9da1449e861882722af50e","tid":2350240,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"黐線勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"沙田me<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2b05b26f2cfa949220348290fdc70dbf266786","tid":